data.description: Are you interested in a starter home, second home or downsizing?  This property offers a split floor plan and was updated in 2023.  It features luxury vinyl flooring throughout, a new walk-in shower in the master bathroom and a new roof.  When you enter through the front door, you'll find a spacious entryway that can be used as a sitting area or dining room with ample space for a large table.  Alternatively, it can serve as a second living room.  Moving on, you'll enter the kitchen/family room combination.  The family room has a sliding glass door that leads to an outdoor living space, which includes a screened lanai and a pool area with enough room for grilling and a picnic table.  Continuing into the fenced backyard, you'll discover a gazebo where you can set up a fire pit and enjoy winter evenings.  The backyard is sizeable enough to accommodate a children's play area and perhaps a horseshoe pit for adult enjoyment!  Many activities such as golfing at the many courses in the area, shopping and restaurants for those days you want to go out and eat.  Numerous beaches from Boca Grande to Manasota Key for you to search for shells or just enjoy the view of the Gulf of Mexico.  Fishing galore for the avid fisherman or kayaking in the intercoastal!  Come and enjoy the enchanted barrier islands and have your piece of Paradise.  This property is also not in a Homeowner's Association. Seller Motivated, all offers to be completed on a Florida contract with signatures and all disclosures submitted as well.
